Lufthansa Will Hire 2,000 Employees This Year, Spiegel Reports

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-03-12T12:53:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-12/lufthansa-will-hire-2-000-employees-this-year-spiegel-reports.html
Deutsche Lufthansa AG plans to hire
more than 2,000 new employees by the end of this year as the
carrier boosts passenger capacity to tap rising demand,  Spiegel 
reported in an article that will be published in the magazine
tomorrow, without saying where it obtained the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  